{"tid":667660,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"比人拖糧 點做好..","createTime":"2018-05-17T02:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T07:53:11.000Z","uid":66684,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5df639a325f3ae2ba03e1652279f53340639bbcb","tid":667660,"uid":66684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T02:42:26.000Z","msg":"事源小弟之前做外判既速遞..之後有一次番工送貨上門 而收貨單位有隻狗咬傷左我 入左院打針睇醫生 之後隔左一星期醫院要我覆疹 公司叫我覆完疹番工..咁我都算啦覆完疹番工 咁我就同我個上頭講話做到夜晚九點半左右收工 （（因為公司有個規矩話啲貨派到夜晚九點半派唔哂就將啲貨入機入唔夠時間派之類既code） 之後個上頭就講左句類似既說話就係我個晚派唔哂啲貨之後都可以唔洗番工之類既說話    咁我話我派埋個晚就唔做 夜晚自己回啲貨番公司 同埋放低啲入code槍   之後而家個上頭死都話搵唔到我支槍 我叫佢睇cctv 佢又唔應我機 咁我想問有咩方法可以追番份糧呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢拖我個期糧都有成萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d8b70cceab144e4729b20c98a7ee2fb18385748","tid":667660,"uid":66684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T02:43:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd75804515877afc39d49f0c81022b174e5299ac","tid":667660,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T02:43:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e8c24b735fdc6929646a6c28bb9b319e737e4d6","tid":667660,"uid":85819,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T02:45:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a4da5679db9954372db17a85a2818cfdd2eea54","tid":667660,"uid":66684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd75804515877afc39d49f0c81022b174e5299ac","tid":667660,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T02:43:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T02:46:31.000Z","msg":"有報 公司叫我報既"},{"pid":"f90d4433a82f638b0ab12994341804d99dda753c","tid":667660,"uid":66684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e8c24b735fdc6929646a6c28bb9b319e73